 Billie Eilish 的《Hit Me Hard And Soft》是双专辑吗？ https://www.nme.com/news/music/is-billie-eilishs-hit-me-hard-and-soft-a-double-album-3757476?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=is-billie-eilishs-软硬兼施的双专辑Alex RigottiSat, 18 May 2024 09:37:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3757476 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什（Chelsea Guglielmino/WireImage 摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《Hit Me Hard And Soft》昨天刚刚发布（5 月 17 日）</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/is-billie-eilishs-hit-me-hard-and-soft-a-double-album-3757476">Billie Eilish 的《Hit Me Hard And Soft》是一张双专辑吗？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什（Chelsea Guglielmino/WireImage 摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billie-Eilish-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>刚刚发行了她的新专辑《Hit Me Hard And Soft》，但根据粉丝的说法，这实际上可能是一张秘密双专辑。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">阅读更多：Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard and Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、明亮</a></li></ul><p>那些听过 Eilish 昨天（5 月 17 日）发行的全新专辑的人可能已经听到了它的最后一句台词：“但是我什么时候可以听到下一张呢？”</p><p>这句话以及其他一些暗示让粉丝相信比莉·艾利什也会做出与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>类似的举动。这位流行歌星最近发行了《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-album-the-anthology-3619877">The Tortured Poets Department</a> 》，并在数小时后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-album-the-anthology-3619877">惊喜地发行了一张名为《The Anthology》的双专辑</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Billie Eilish 可能会发行一张双专辑，作为《HIT ME HARD AND SOFT》片尾的一句话：</p><p> “但是我什么时候才能听到下一首” <a href="https://t.co/8BTboyadY6">pic.twitter.com/8BTboyadY6</a></p><p> - 比莉·艾利什日报 (@billieeilishdly) <a href="https://twitter.com/billieeilishdly/status/1790561992069296333?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>最重要的是，粉丝们认为艾利什对色彩的使用可能是双专辑的第二个暗示。为了调侃“Hit Me Hard And Soft”，艾利什使用了大量的蓝色，无论是在她的专辑封面上还是在宣传她的唱片的广告牌上。</p><p>然而，艾利什也穿着特定明亮色调的红色衣服，这让粉丝们相信这可能不仅仅是“Hit Me”那么引人注目。这些颜色也将与游戏“ilomilo”的两个主角相匹配，Eilish 甚至在她的首张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/billie-eilish-album-review-when-we-all-fall-asleep-where-do-we-go-2467653">When We All Fall AsleepWhere Do We Go</a> ”中写了一首关于该游戏的歌曲。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">你会告诉我没有。双专辑？？？ <a href="https://t.co/vmqiHY7Rvg">pic.twitter.com/vmqiHY7Rvg</a></p><p> — bri ✩ 爱比莉<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1f5-1f1f8.png" alt="🇵🇸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@BBITTERSUITE） <a href="https://twitter.com/BBITTERSUITE/status/1790545834469371981?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 5 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在回顾昨天发布的《Hit Me》时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826"><em>NME</em>给了它四颗星，</a>并写道：“Billie 带着寻找自我的愿望进入了这个过程，无论是创造性的还是个人的：《Hit Me Hard and Soft》仍然是独特的，是一个独特才华的写照。进入青年期，探索自己的酷儿特质，体验追逐激情或坠入爱河的情感刺激和（有时）灾难。</p><p> “在尝试为自己写一张专辑时，她制作的专辑比她以前做过的任何专辑都更能引起共鸣。”</p><p>在其他地方，艾利什和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">芬尼斯</a>谈到了这张专辑， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-and-finneas-have-never-ever-ever-loved-something-more-than-new-album-hit-me-hard-and-soft-3757252">称他们“从未如此热爱过任何东西”。</a> “Finneas 和我在这张专辑中投入了如此多的精力，从来没有像现在这样热爱过任何东西，”Eilish 在 Instagram 上发帖写道。 “我们希望你非常喜欢它，我会在另一边见到你 EEEEEEEEEEEK HMHAS 现在到处爱你们都爱死了！！！” </p><p><iframe title="比莉·艾利什 |第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mVvt33l7BwM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他消息中，Eilish 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">宣布了 2024-2025 年“HIT ME HARD AND SOFT”世界巡演</a>- 定于今年秋天开始。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处购买美国门票</a>，访问此处购买<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F22