ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Noah-Kahan-Lewis-Capaldi-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Noah-Kahan-Lewis-Capaldi-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Noah-Kahan-Lewis-Capaldi-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Noah-Kahan-Lewis-Capaldi-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>粉丝们发现<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lewis-capaldi">刘易斯·卡帕尔迪 (Lewis Capaldi)</a>在因心理健康问题而中断后，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan)</a>一起回到了录音室。</p><p>大约一年前，卡帕尔迪在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">2023 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>的演出后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lewis-capaldi-mental-health-break-following-glastonbury-set-3460913">宣布，他将暂时退出</a>音乐界，这场演出让他<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/glastonbury/lewis-capaldi-struggles-with-voice-during-glastonbury-performance-3460578">多次因嗓子问题而困扰。</a>今年一月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lewis-capaldi-shares-health-update-and-announces-extended-version-of-album-3564312">他更新了自己的健康状况</a>，称“一切进展顺利！”</p><p>现在，这位苏格兰艺术家似乎可能会推出一些新音乐，这要归功于突破性民谣明星诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan) 在 Instagram 上发布的帖子。在卡汉昨天（5 月 17 日）发布的一组照片中，第三张图片中卡帕尔迪被标记为戴着耳机，显然是在录音室里。</p><p>卡汉在他的帖子中写道：“没有什么可报告的，但我希望你感到无聊并前往北方” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7CJnHZuQEQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div styl