 AC/DC 八年来首次巡演在德国开启，演出曲目涵盖职业生涯https://www.nme.com/news/music/ac-dc-kick-off-first-tour-for-eight-years-with-career-spanning-setlist-in-germany-3757468?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=ac-dc-在德国开启八年首次巡演并涵盖职业生涯跨越曲目列表Emma WilkesSat, 18 May 2024 09:07:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3757468 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布赖恩·约翰逊" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该节目也是乐队首次与新贝斯手 Chris Chaney 合作</p><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ac-dc-kick-off-first-tour-for-eight-years-with-career-spanning-setlist-in-germany-3757468">AC/DC 八年来首次巡演后，他们在德国的演出曲目</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布赖恩·约翰逊" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/brian-johnson-gina-wetzler-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>昨晚（5月17日）在德国拉开了大型欧洲体育场巡演的序幕，这是他们时隔8年再次回归巡演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ac-dc-comeback-album-power-up-interview-malcolm-young-woke-2800458">AC/DC 谈他们爆炸性的复出唱片《Power Up》：“这张专辑是献给 Malcolm 的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这次巡演是为了支持他们 2020 年的复出唱片《Power Up》，在盖尔森基兴可容纳 62,000 人的 Veltins-Arena 举行，这是新贝斯手 Chris Chaney 首次以新贝斯手 Chris Chaney 为主角，Chris Chaney 因在<a href="https://www.nme.com/arttists/jane's-addiction">《Jane&#39;s Addiction》</a>中的任期而闻名。巡演退役后，他接替了克里夫·威廉姆斯。</p><p>他们的歌单几乎与十月份 Power Trip Festival 复出演出的歌单几乎相同，尽管有些歌曲的顺序发生了变化。乐队以“If You Want Blood (You&#39;ve Got It)”和“Back In Black”拉开了他们职业生涯的序幕，并以传统的结束曲“For those About To Rock (We Salute You)”结束。</p><p>查看他们的演出片段和下面的演出列表： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="AC/DC INTRO + IF YOU WANT BLOOD 盖尔森基兴现场演出。 2024 年 5 月 17 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/e999Dhb5IHw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="AC/DC - 黑色回归 - 盖尔森基兴 2024 年（第一晚）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RdiBPm3i3WU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><strong>设置列表（通过<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlist/acdc/2024/veltins-arena-gelsenkirchen-germany-23abb82b.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Setlist.fm</em></a> ）：</strong></p><p> <strong>“如果你想要鲜血（你已经得到了）”</strong><br /> <strong>《黑衣归来》</strong><br /